These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Job: scientist, designer, accountant, analyst
Nationality: nigerian, thai, argentine, italian
1. Job:designer is between Job:scientist and Nationality:thai##2
2. Job:designer is on the left or right of Nationality:nigerian##3
3. Job:designer is somewhere between Job:analyst and Job:scientist##7
4. Nationality:thai is in an even position##4
5. Job:analyst is on the right of Nationality:argentine##1
6. Nationality:thai is somewhere to the left of Nationality:nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Job   | accountant | analyst       | designer | scientist        |
| Nationality      | argentine  | thai | italian        | nigerian |

