2. Color:blue is somewhere to the left of Color:green##5
3. Color:blue is somewhere to the right of House:victorian##5
4. Color:ebony is on the left of Color:blue##1
5. House:victorian is between House:craftsman and House:cottage##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Color     | lavender | ebony       | blue         | green     |
| House   | cottage   | victorian | craftsman | palace |

