.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Color: apricot, red, azure, white
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, adventure, animation
1. Movie-Genre:animation is on the far left or far right##3
2. Color:apricot is somewhere between Movie-Genre:musical and Color:white##7
3. Color:azure == Movie-Genre:animation##1
4. Movie-Genre:adventure is on the left of Movie-Genre:animation##1
5. Color:red is on the left of Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Color   | red | apricot | white       | azure |
| Movie-Genre   | musical      | crime   | adventure | animation  |

