3. Food:pumpkin is on the right of Food:blueberry##1
4. Flower:dahlia is somewhere between Food:spinach and Food:pumpkin##7
5. Flower:dahlia is on the left of Flower:aconite##1
6. Flower:sunflower is somewhere to the left of Flower:dahlia##5
7. Food:spinach is on the far left or far right##3
8. Food:pumpkin is on the left or right of Food:blueberry##3

